2006;;Aruba;;Canadian;;Hubert Davis;;A.J. Saudin, Devon Bostick;;short film;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aruba_(film);;Milan (A.J. Saudin) is an 11-year-old boy who dreams about escaping a violent home life. When his parents fight or take drugs, or when bullies pick on him in school, he finds peace in contemplating a postcard with an idyllic picture of the island of Aruba, and imagines himself in that faraway place as a way to survive.